[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32135_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32135/5147_32135_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "THE CENTRAL AMERICAN AND MEXICAN COLONIES.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32135_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32135/5147_32135_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Who brought the dialect of Homer to America? or who took to Greece that of the Mayas? Greek is the offspring of the Sanscrit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32135_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32135/5147_32135_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They wrote on cotton cloth, on skins prepared like parchment, on a composition of silk and gum, and on a species of paper, soft and beautiful, made from the aloe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32135_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32135/5147_32135_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Cotton napkins and ewers of water were placed before them as they took their seats at the board.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They claimed descent from \"the twelve great gods,\" which must have meant the twelve gods of Atlantis, to wit, Poseidon and Cleito and their ten sons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "The great similarity between the Egyptian civilization and that of the American nations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "six.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They were not likely to send ships to Atlantis.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "We find another proof of the descent of the Egyptians from Atlantis in their belief as to the \"under world.\" This land of the dead was situated in the West-hence the tombs were all placed, whenever possible, on the west bank of the Nile.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "The constant cry of the mourners as the funeral procession moved forward was, \"To the west; to the west.\" This under world was beyond the water, hence the funeral procession always crossed a body of water.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "In connection with all this we must not forget that Plato described Atlantis as \"that sacred island lying beneath the sun\" Everywhere in the ancient world we find the minds of men looking to the west for the land of the dead.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Poole says, \"How then can we account for this strong conviction?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "There is no evidence that the civilization of Egypt was developed in Egypt itself; it must have been transported there from some other country.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "To use the words of a recent writer in Blackwood,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "\"As we have not yet discovered any trace of the rude, savage Egypt, but have seen her in her very earliest manifestations already skilful, erudite, and strong, it is impossible to determine the order of her inventions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Light may yet be thrown upon her rise and progress, but our deepest researches have hitherto shown her to us as only the mother of a most accomplished race.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "The explanation is simple: the waters of the Atlantic now flow over the country where all this magnificence and power were developed by slow stages from the rude beginnings of barbarism.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "And how mighty must have been the parent nation of which this Egypt was a colony!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Look at the magnificent mason work of this ancient people!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000022_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000022_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Look at the Temple of Karnac, covering a square each side of which is eighteen hundred feet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "\"When we consider the high ideal of the Egyptians, as proved by their portrayals of a just life, the principles they laid down as the basis of ethics, the elevation of women among them, their humanity in war, we must admit that their moral place ranks very high among the nations of antiquity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Then look at the proficiency in art of this ancient people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They were the first mathematicians of the Old World.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Those Greeks whom we regard as the fathers of mathematics were simply pupils of Egypt. They were the first land surveyors.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They were the first astronomers, calculating eclipses, and watching the periods of planets and constellations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They knew the rotundity of the earth, which it was supposed Columbus had discovered!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Professor Mitchell, to whom the fact was communicated, employed his assistants to ascertain the exact position of the heavenly bodies belonging to our solar system on the equinox of that year.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They were the first agriculturists of the Old World, raising all the cereals, cattle, horses, sheep, etc",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They worked in gold, silver, copper, bronze, and iron; they tempered iron to the hardness of steel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "They were the first chemists.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "The word \"chemistry\" comes from chemi, and chemi means Egypt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "Their dentists filled teeth with gold; their farmers hatched poultry by artificial heat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "This papyrus is a medical treatise; there are in it no incantations or charms; but it deals in reasonable remedies, draughts, unguents and injections.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000032_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000032_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "The later medical papyri contain a great deal of magic and incantations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "\"Among the ancient cultured nations of Egypt and Assyria handicrafts had already come to a stage which could only have been reached by thousands of years of progress.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5147/32136/5147_32136_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5147",
        "content": "In museums still may be examined the work of their joiners, stone cutters, goldsmiths, wonderful in skill and finish, and in putting to shame the modern artificer....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5147_32136_000038_000002",
